1
00:00:10,469 --> 00:00:11,303
JUJUTSU KAISEN

2
00:00:34,451 --> 00:00:35,661
(JUJUTSU KAISEN THE
CULLING GAME PART 1)

3
00:01:39,349 --> 00:01:42,435
(JUJUTSU KAISEN)

4
00:01:42,436 --> 00:01:45,021
I was wondering who it was.

5
00:01:45,022 --> 00:01:46,689
That face is a mess.

6
00:01:46,690 --> 00:01:48,524
And it can't be healed, can it?

7
00:01:48,525 --> 00:01:50,652
What are you going
to do now, Maki?

8
00:01:51,361 --> 00:01:54,238
I didn't know you could tell
women apart by their faces.

9
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:56,617
I thought you only
had eyes for butts.

10
00:02:05,876 --> 00:02:08,503
I'm asking you what
you're going to do next.

11
00:02:08,504 --> 00:02:10,047
Answer me, you piece of trash.

12
00:02:10,756 --> 00:02:13,674
You can't use jujutsu
or see cursed spirits.

13
00:02:13,675 --> 00:02:15,760
Even the only thing decent
about you, your face is ruined.

14
00:02:15,761 --> 00:02:18,889
No one will take you
seriously anymore.

15
00:02:20,307 --> 00:02:22,683
How lonely.

16
00:02:22,684 --> 00:02:25,604
Do you want me to
bully you like before?

17
00:02:27,606 --> 00:02:29,106
What now?

18
00:02:29,107 --> 00:02:32,361
Are you going to follow
Okkotsu and Megumi around?

19
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:37,658
Say something, you trash.

20
00:02:38,158 --> 00:02:40,327
Maki, turn back now.

21
00:02:41,036 --> 00:02:42,662
Did you forget?

22
00:02:42,663 --> 00:02:46,625
We're not allowed in
the cursed warehouse.

23
00:02:47,584 --> 00:02:50,045
But the head of the
Zen'in family agreed to it.

24
00:02:51,421 --> 00:02:53,841
The head of the
Zen'in family? Me?

25
00:02:55,050 --> 00:02:57,635
Yes, it was Naobito's will.

26
00:02:57,636 --> 00:02:59,762
I refuse. It's too
much of a hassle.

27
00:02:59,763 --> 00:03:02,431
No can do, I'm sorry.
Please accept it.

28
00:03:02,432 --> 00:03:03,432
Naobito stated

29
00:03:03,433 --> 00:03:07,144
that he would hand over all of
the Zen'in family's assets to you.

30
00:03:07,145 --> 00:03:08,688
Including money
and cursed tools.

31
00:03:08,689 --> 00:03:09,814
If you become the
head of the family,

32
00:03:09,815 --> 00:03:12,817
you'll get information on the Big
Three Families and the higher-ups.

33
00:03:12,818 --> 00:03:15,570
This will greatly affect
our future activities.

34
00:03:15,571 --> 00:03:17,655
Then you be the head.

35
00:03:17,656 --> 00:03:18,906
I'll give it to you.

36
00:03:18,907 --> 00:03:21,367
No one will acknowledge
me as I am now.

37
00:03:21,368 --> 00:03:23,077
Or follow me.

38
00:03:23,078 --> 00:03:25,621
You've inherited the
family's cursed technique.

39
00:03:25,622 --> 00:03:27,832
You've even mastered
Domain Expansion.

40
00:03:27,833 --> 00:03:29,625
And Satoru values you.

41
00:03:29,626 --> 00:03:32,004
Only you, with such a
good hand, can barely be it.

42
00:03:33,964 --> 00:03:35,423
What do you mean, acknowledge?

43
00:03:35,424 --> 00:03:39,302
It doesn't matter what the
Zen'in family thinks, right?

44
00:03:39,303 --> 00:03:40,636
The benefits I
mentioned just now

45
00:03:40,637 --> 00:03:42,973
can be obtained if you become
the head of the family, right?

46
00:03:44,516 --> 00:03:47,269
I'm not qualified yet.

47
00:03:49,605 --> 00:03:53,150
I... can't create a
sanctuary for Mai.

48
00:03:57,196 --> 00:03:58,779
I understand.

49
00:03:58,780 --> 00:04:02,534
Come back!

50
00:04:07,706 --> 00:04:09,332
Why?

51
00:04:09,333 --> 00:04:12,836
Why are you always like this?

52
00:04:17,424 --> 00:04:18,758
Just for once,

53
00:04:18,759 --> 00:04:21,010
make me glad I
gave birth to you.

54
00:04:21,011 --> 00:04:22,346
Maki.

55
00:04:38,862 --> 00:04:40,030
Dad.

56
00:04:41,198 --> 00:04:44,367
If that was your plan, why
didn't you say so earlier?

57
00:04:44,368 --> 00:04:46,827
You were too impatient.

58
00:04:46,828 --> 00:04:50,164
It seems Megumi Fushiguro
is more capable than you.

59
00:04:50,165 --> 00:04:51,541
What?

60
00:04:51,542 --> 00:04:53,918
Many people support him.

61
00:04:53,919 --> 00:04:56,754
They want to use this to repair
their relationship with the Gojo family.

62
00:04:56,755 --> 00:04:59,674
However, giving all the
assets to Megumi Fushiguro

63
00:04:59,675 --> 00:05:02,093
is something we cannot accept.

64
00:05:02,094 --> 00:05:04,095
Then what's taking them so long?

65
00:05:04,096 --> 00:05:08,599
It's not just the Gojo family.
Megumi Fushiguro and

66
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:12,228
Noritoshi Kamo, the next head of
the Kamo family, are on good terms.

67
00:05:12,229 --> 00:05:16,357
If we eliminate him for no reason,
the Zen'in family's position will worsen.

68
00:05:16,358 --> 00:05:18,359
Satoru Gojo is sealed.

69
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:20,862
The power struggle is
ever-changing, and we'll fall behind.

70
00:05:20,863 --> 00:05:22,321
Of course, I know that.

71
00:05:22,322 --> 00:05:23,447
But why now?

72
00:05:23,448 --> 00:05:26,242
You didn't pay attention to the notice
from the Jujutsu Headquarters, did you?

73
00:05:26,243 --> 00:05:28,245
(2. LIST GOJO AS CO-PERPETRATOR)
There's no reason not to make use of this.

74
00:05:28,495 --> 00:05:30,329
(OF THE SHIBUYA INCIDENT) Megumi
Fushiguro, Maki, and Mai are deemed

75
00:05:30,330 --> 00:05:33,165
(EXILE HIM FROM JUJUTSU SOCIETY)
rebels for attempting to free Satoru Gojo

76
00:05:33,166 --> 00:05:35,043
(IT'S A CRIME TO UNSEAL
GOJO) and will be killed.

77
00:05:36,378 --> 00:05:40,131
After all, killing your own
daughters makes it more justifiable.

78
00:05:40,132 --> 00:05:41,048
Yes.

79
00:05:41,049 --> 00:05:44,511
This way, we can gain more
trust from the Jujutsu Headquarters.

80
00:05:44,887 --> 00:05:48,347
But will Uncle Ogi accept this?

81
00:05:48,348 --> 00:05:49,682
This was Ogi's suggestion.

82
00:05:49,683 --> 00:05:52,476
There are no more
cursed tools here, Maki.

83
00:05:52,477 --> 00:05:55,898
We saw through your moves
and cleared them out beforehand.

84
00:05:59,484 --> 00:06:01,528
Why are you here?

85
00:06:02,029 --> 00:06:03,238
Idiot.

86
00:06:10,204 --> 00:06:14,208
(JUZO KUMIYA'S
MASTERPIECE, "DRAGONBONE")

87
00:06:17,961 --> 00:06:19,546
(ESOTERIC TECHNIQUE
"FALLING BLOSSOM EMOTION")

88
00:06:21,089 --> 00:06:24,050
Do you know why I wasn't
made the head of the family,

89
00:06:24,051 --> 00:06:27,303
but my brother Naobito was?

90
00:06:27,304 --> 00:06:30,432
Because you're a
bastard who kills children.

91
00:06:45,697 --> 00:06:48,908
Why didn't I become the head?

92
00:06:48,909 --> 00:06:49,743
Why?

93
00:06:50,285 --> 00:06:52,411
It's because of you kids.

94
00:06:52,412 --> 00:06:53,412
It should have broken.

95
00:06:53,413 --> 00:06:54,914
You're so useless.

96
00:06:54,915 --> 00:06:55,916
The blade...

97
00:07:07,094 --> 00:07:08,886
You think that by
breaking the blade,

98
00:07:08,887 --> 00:07:11,138
you're shortening
the attack range,

99
00:07:11,139 --> 00:07:13,307
and that's why you
got too close to me?

100
00:07:13,308 --> 00:07:15,519
That's why you're useless.

101
00:07:16,186 --> 00:07:18,646
I'm not a swordsman,
but a sorcerer.

102
00:07:18,647 --> 00:07:21,524
You're just a defect, yet you want to
measure me by your own standards.

103
00:07:21,525 --> 00:07:23,192
How ridiculous.

104
00:07:23,193 --> 00:07:25,027
I'll say it as many
times as you want.

105
00:07:25,028 --> 00:07:27,655
The reason I wasn't
chosen as the previous head

106
00:07:27,656 --> 00:07:29,782
is because of you two.

107
00:07:29,783 --> 00:07:32,660
The history of my brother's
cursed technique is short.

108
00:07:32,661 --> 00:07:36,581
Whether it's family-inherited
or not isn't even the issue.

109
00:07:36,582 --> 00:07:38,040
As a sorcerer,

110
00:07:38,041 --> 00:07:42,837
my brother only outdo
me in one aspect.

111
00:07:42,838 --> 00:07:45,507
That is the quality
of our children.

112
00:07:46,300 --> 00:07:51,095
Children must never
hold their parents back.

113
00:07:51,096 --> 00:07:52,805
Don't you know that?

114
00:07:52,806 --> 00:07:56,351
In this country, holding
each other back is a virtue.

115
00:08:04,568 --> 00:08:08,070
This is a training
and punishment room.

116
00:08:08,071 --> 00:08:11,240
Countless Grade 2 or lower
cursed spirits are kept here.

117
00:08:11,241 --> 00:08:13,409
Cursed spirits are
afraid of me now.

118
00:08:13,410 --> 00:08:16,663
But they will crawl
out and eat you soon.

119
00:08:17,789 --> 00:08:21,250
Heavenly Restriction,
physical prowess.

120
00:08:21,251 --> 00:08:23,169
So what?

121
00:08:23,170 --> 00:08:28,926
We sorcerers train our bodies every day
and use cursed energy to strengthen them.

122
00:08:29,384 --> 00:08:30,801
Maki.

123
00:08:30,802 --> 00:08:32,553
That ability of yours...

124
00:08:32,554 --> 00:08:35,349
Every one of us has it.

125
00:08:36,642 --> 00:08:38,226
Farewell,

126
00:08:38,227 --> 00:08:40,771
the stain on my life.

127
00:09:16,557 --> 00:09:19,893
You're so tenacious.

128
00:09:23,605 --> 00:09:25,439
I knew it.

129
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:28,819
This would happen one day.

130
00:09:43,333 --> 00:09:44,459
This is the worst.

131
00:10:11,612 --> 00:10:16,032
You should know my
cursed technique by now.

132
00:10:16,033 --> 00:10:19,786
I can't create anything
too big or complicated.

133
00:10:23,290 --> 00:10:26,417
Besides, I was
just slashed by him.

134
00:10:26,418 --> 00:10:28,712
I'll die after this.

135
00:10:29,463 --> 00:10:30,672
I'm going first.

136
00:10:31,757 --> 00:10:33,466
You're on your own now.

137
00:10:33,467 --> 00:10:35,844
Hey, Mai. Wait.

138
00:10:36,970 --> 00:10:38,054
What are you talking about?

139
00:10:38,055 --> 00:10:39,598
Just come back.

140
00:10:40,557 --> 00:10:43,851
I've known this for a long time.

141
00:10:43,852 --> 00:10:47,481
Why are twins a bad
omen for jujutsu sorcerers?

142
00:10:48,815 --> 00:10:52,276
If you want something,
you have to pay a price for it.

143
00:10:52,277 --> 00:10:55,154
It's not limited
to Binding Vows.

144
00:10:55,155 --> 00:10:58,617
It's the same as getting
stronger after suffering.

145
00:11:00,744 --> 00:11:02,286
But for us,

146
00:11:02,287 --> 00:11:05,832
this kind of relationship
is not always valid.

147
00:11:07,334 --> 00:11:10,294
Because in jujutsu,

148
00:11:10,295 --> 00:11:13,423
identical twins are seen
as the same person.

149
00:11:14,091 --> 00:11:15,258
Do you understand?

150
00:11:15,259 --> 00:11:18,511
You are me, and I am you.

151
00:11:18,512 --> 00:11:21,180
Even if you throw up blood

152
00:11:21,181 --> 00:11:24,600
trying to become
stronger, it's meaningless.

153
00:11:24,601 --> 00:11:27,646
Because I don't
want to get stronger.

154
00:11:29,273 --> 00:11:31,774
If you don't have
a cursed technique,

155
00:11:31,775 --> 00:11:34,277
it's useless if I'm
the only one with it.

156
00:11:34,278 --> 00:11:36,571
As long as I'm here, Maki,

157
00:11:36,572 --> 00:11:38,281
you'll always be a half-baked.

158
00:11:38,282 --> 00:11:39,533
I get it!

159
00:11:40,701 --> 00:11:41,785
Come back!

160
00:11:42,911 --> 00:11:44,871
I'll keep only this.

161
00:11:44,872 --> 00:11:46,456
You can throw away the rest.

162
00:11:50,252 --> 00:11:52,461
Be it cursed energy
or anything else,

163
00:11:52,462 --> 00:11:54,965
I'll take it all away for you.

164
00:11:55,841 --> 00:11:58,594
Just promise me one thing.

165
00:12:00,345 --> 00:12:02,848
Destroy everything.

166
00:12:05,601 --> 00:12:06,977
All of it.

167
00:12:09,313 --> 00:12:10,689
My sister.

168
00:12:17,070 --> 00:12:21,199
Mai...

169
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,825
Wake up...

170
00:12:22,826 --> 00:12:24,285
Mai.

171
00:12:24,286 --> 00:12:26,204
Wake up!

172
00:12:26,205 --> 00:12:27,955
Mai!

173
00:12:27,956 --> 00:12:29,374
Wake up...

174
00:12:31,460 --> 00:12:35,463
Mai...

175
00:12:35,464 --> 00:12:37,299
Wake up...

176
00:12:38,425 --> 00:12:42,136
Mai... Wake up...

177
00:12:42,137 --> 00:12:43,347
Mai...

178
00:12:47,935 --> 00:12:50,728
It's a reaction to the
cursed spirit's annihilation.

179
00:12:50,729 --> 00:12:52,063
What's going on?

180
00:12:52,064 --> 00:12:54,607
My body still remembers.

181
00:12:54,608 --> 00:12:56,859
It's something I
wanted to forget.

182
00:12:56,860 --> 00:12:58,320
That fear.

183
00:13:00,531 --> 00:13:03,783
Cursed technique,
Blazing Courage!

184
00:13:03,784 --> 00:13:05,326
I'll fight you!

185
00:13:05,327 --> 00:13:07,078
With my own hands,

186
00:13:07,079 --> 00:13:09,957
I'll burn you to
ashes once again!

187
00:13:12,626 --> 00:13:13,876
Come here!

188
00:13:13,877 --> 00:13:15,754
You useless--

189
00:13:26,181 --> 00:13:29,893
Mai, let's get started.

190
00:13:36,859 --> 00:13:39,945
(EPISODE 51 THE
PERFECT PREPARATION)

191
00:13:42,781 --> 00:13:44,950
(JUJUTSU KAISEN)

192
00:13:48,245 --> 00:13:50,289
What's with all the noise?

193
00:13:53,125 --> 00:13:54,292
Mr. Jinichi!

194
00:13:54,293 --> 00:13:55,918
Maki has lost her mind.

195
00:13:55,919 --> 00:13:57,378
She killed Mr. Ogi.

196
00:13:57,379 --> 00:13:59,964
The Kukuru Unit
is handling it now.

197
00:13:59,965 --> 00:14:01,382
No matter how good Mr. Ogi is,

198
00:14:01,383 --> 00:14:05,261
it's normal to miss an attack while
sleeping or using the bathroom.

199
00:14:05,262 --> 00:14:07,096
Capture her before I get there.

200
00:14:07,097 --> 00:14:08,181
Yes, sir.

201
00:14:08,182 --> 00:14:12,728
If you dawdle, I'll be the one
getting yelled at by Jinichi.

202
00:14:13,604 --> 00:14:14,520
Don't kill her.

203
00:14:14,521 --> 00:14:15,438
(KUKURU UNIT, CAPTAIN,
NOBUAKI ZEN'IN) Don't kill her.

204
00:14:15,439 --> 00:14:16,355
(KUKURU UNIT, CAPTAIN,
NOBUAKI ZEN'IN) I'll wrap things up.

205
00:14:16,356 --> 00:14:17,690
- The "Kukuru Unit" is
comprised -Do you hear me?

206
00:14:17,691 --> 00:14:22,153
- of Zen'in men without jujutsu.
- Hurry up!

207
00:14:22,154 --> 00:14:23,821
As a subordinate
organization of the Hei,

208
00:14:23,822 --> 00:14:26,199
- they undergo martial arts training.
- Found her!

209
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,200
She's in the Room of Tonnage.

210
00:14:27,201 --> 00:14:28,284
What are you going to do?

211
00:14:28,285 --> 00:14:30,244
What was I going to do?

212
00:14:30,245 --> 00:14:33,164
We can see her holding
two unknown cursed tools.

213
00:14:33,165 --> 00:14:35,249
Before Maki went
to Jujutsu High,

214
00:14:35,250 --> 00:14:36,919
she was also in the Kukuru Unit.

215
00:14:37,211 --> 00:14:41,255
Why won't you fall with me?

216
00:14:41,256 --> 00:14:42,465
That's right.

217
00:14:42,466 --> 00:14:43,842
Round her up!

218
00:14:44,176 --> 00:14:45,843
Now that I think about it,

219
00:14:45,844 --> 00:14:48,180
that was the right
answer for us.

220
00:14:49,181 --> 00:14:50,015
I'm sorry.

221
00:14:50,682 --> 00:14:52,350
I'm sorry, Mai.

222
00:14:52,351 --> 00:14:53,643
Surround her!

223
00:14:53,644 --> 00:14:54,561
Promise me.

224
00:14:55,729 --> 00:14:58,440
Destroy everything.

225
00:15:06,782 --> 00:15:08,450
All of it.

226
00:17:26,463 --> 00:17:28,966
How did it go?

227
00:17:31,510 --> 00:17:33,387
You scared me.

228
00:18:01,331 --> 00:18:03,417
It's Chojuro's cursed technique.

229
00:18:04,293 --> 00:18:06,043
Has the Hei made their move?

230
00:18:06,044 --> 00:18:07,044
The Hei,

231
00:18:07,045 --> 00:18:09,005
(THE "HEI") based on
Jujutsu High qualifications,

232
00:18:09,006 --> 00:18:12,925
(THE "HEI") all of them
are Semi-Grade 1 or above.

233
00:18:12,926 --> 00:18:13,843
(THE "HEI") They
are the Zen'in family's

234
00:18:13,844 --> 00:18:15,846
strongest group of sorcerers.

235
00:18:29,443 --> 00:18:31,235
How is she still moving

236
00:18:31,236 --> 00:18:32,487
after being attacked by Chojuro?

237
00:18:36,825 --> 00:18:37,950
She's fast.

238
00:18:37,951 --> 00:18:39,411
Even my cursed energy
defense was easily...

239
00:18:42,247 --> 00:18:43,873
Is she really...

240
00:18:43,874 --> 00:18:45,083
that Maki?

241
00:19:01,016 --> 00:19:02,267
Mr. Jinichi!

242
00:19:03,060 --> 00:19:04,727
Keep suppressing her!

243
00:19:04,728 --> 00:19:05,729
Ranta!

244
00:19:15,906 --> 00:19:18,283
I... I can't hold her down!

245
00:19:22,412 --> 00:19:24,248
Don't worry about
me, Mr. Jinichi!

246
00:19:24,790 --> 00:19:26,415
The Zen'in Clan only exists now

247
00:19:26,416 --> 00:19:28,251
because Mr. Toji
wasn't interested.

248
00:19:28,252 --> 00:19:29,794
You've noticed, haven't you?

249
00:19:29,795 --> 00:19:32,922
Maki is just like him now!

250
00:19:32,923 --> 00:19:34,173
Right now,

251
00:19:34,174 --> 00:19:35,675
right here,

252
00:19:35,676 --> 00:19:38,220
you must kill her!

253
00:20:06,582 --> 00:20:10,586
You did it, Mr. Jinichi.

254
00:20:26,476 --> 00:20:28,061
You're so cruel.

255
00:20:28,937 --> 00:20:31,607
(HEAD OF THE HEI, NAOYA ZEN'IN)
Do you have a conscience?

256
00:20:33,483 --> 00:20:34,567
No.

257
00:20:34,568 --> 00:20:36,778
Because that guy took it all.

258
00:20:37,863 --> 00:20:41,574
Everyone says I'm a genius.

259
00:20:41,575 --> 00:20:43,994
They say I'm the next
head of the Zen'in family.

